-- Fed joined G7 in yen intervention: NY Fed spokesman
-- 
-- Fri Mar 18, 2011 10:30am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/03/18/us-usa-fed-idUSTRE72E10D20110318

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - The U.S. Federal Reserve joined other Group of Seven central banks in intervening in currency markets to help weaken the Japanese yen on Friday, a New York Federal Reserve spokesman told Reuters. 

 (Reporting by  Kristina Cooke , Editing by Chizu Nomiyama)